title: 677: FIDELITY PROJECTS $1 MILLION BITCOIN PRICE IN 2026!! HOW $1M BTC WILL DRIVE BILLIONAIRE FLIPPENING!!
description:
Asset management giant Fidelity, who currently holds $10.4 trillion in assets under management, projects a $1 million Bitcoin price by 2026, according to Jurrien Timmer, the director of Global Macro at Fidelity Investments.

The explosion in wealth that will occur as BTC gains in value will create a new class of billionaires.
